Vintage Elegance: Our bookcase with tree structure is full of natural atmosphere and vintage color scheme makes it become a piece of charming decorative furniture in any place. It can be a scene of its own, letting you feel the exotic flavor

Easy to Install and Clean: We will provide detailed instructions and accessories so that you can assemble this tree bookshelf quickly and easily to shorten your installation time. The smooth surface makes it easy to clean with a towel to wipe

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars They want you to conquer!
reviews.reviewText: So, I’ve bought hundreds of self-assembly products in my lifetime. But these guys, they made it fool proof. They are like your kindergarten gym teacher that knows you are too weak to do a pull up on your own, but they know you need the encouragement to persevere now so that life doesn’t overwhelm your soul later.First, the instructions were simple….just a picture and associated letters of the parts. “Come on buddy, see how easy it is? You’ve got this, Champ.”Second, I wasn’t missing a SINGLE piece. “You’ve got everything you need inside of you Sport.”Finally, the way it all fits and ultimately tightens together is absolutely ingenious. “See, Tiger, I knew you could do it!”It was a spiritual experience.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Got this for my daughter. She was shocked at how mamy books it held. She put it together easily by herself (she is in college). It looks good and not too cheaply made.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I LOVE this bookshelf! The design is interesting and visually appealing. The wood was free from scratches and defects. Assembly took 30-40 minutes or so and wasn't difficult. I required help because of a shoulder injury, but it could easily be done with one set of hands. Instructions were simple and easy to understand.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute way to display my books!
reviews.reviewText: Very cute shelf. Assembly took maybe half hour or so - LOTS of screws to put in… and most are going into wood, so utilizing an impact driver is essential. Shelf seems like it may be a bit too heavy, so would recommend utilizing the wall anchor. All the wood on the shelf look great, no scratches or defects in the finish that I could tell. Would definitely recommend
